name: Blow Parried
Lore: 'Offense may win battles, but defense keeps you alive long enough to mount an offense.',
Text: 'Take top card of Force Pile into hand. OR If opponent just revealed a combat card, it is canceled (place in opponent''s Used Pile) and opponent must draw destiny instead (that destiny is reduced by 1). OR Cancel Glancing Blow, Clash Of Sabers, or Obi-Wan''s Journal.',
